===Redirected magic tablets===
[[Teleport to house (tablet)|Teleport to house]] tablets can be redirected using [[Scroll of redirection|scrolls of redirection]] to one of the [[POH portal|player-owned house portals]] or to [[Trollheim]], provided the player has a sufficient [[Construction]] level. This makes the tablet '''untradeable'''. This process can be reverted at any time. However, [[Scroll of redirection|scrolls of redirection]] are not returned to the player when the process is reverted.

Based on the expected value of spending [[Nightmare Zone]] reward points on [[herb box]]es, redirected teleport to house tablets have a value of {{NoCoins|{{GEP|Teleport to house (tablet)}} + (775 * (10 * ({{GEP|Grimy guam leaf|32/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy marrentill|24/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy tarromin|18/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy harralander|14/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy ranarr weed|11/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy irit leaf|8/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy avantoe|6/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy kwuarm|5/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy cadantine|4/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy lantadyme|3/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy dwarf weed|3/128}}) / 9500)) round 0|c}}.

